    <item>
      <title>Rivers</title>
      <link>https://mlahariya.github.io/writingprojects/poetry_1/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://mlahariya.github.io/writingprojects/poetry_1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Rivers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All flowing &lt;br&gt;
All muddy &lt;br&gt;
All deep &lt;br&gt;
All hollow &lt;br&gt;
All running freely to the ocean under the skies &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All rivers &lt;br&gt;
Start the same &lt;br&gt;
Survive the same &lt;br&gt;
End the same &lt;br&gt;
Cliche love stories of &lt;br&gt;
Waterbodies &lt;br&gt;
Meeting &lt;br&gt;
Waterbodies. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready?&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
